INSERT INTO `joebloggs_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2014-01-14 16:02:58','2014-01-14 16:02:58','Welcome to your ePortfolio.\r\n\r\nNormally, to log in to your ePortfolio you click the link provided by your institution which will log you in automatically. If you have not been given a link you will have been provided with a password which you should use with the username <em>admin</em> to log in.\r\n\r\nPlease change your email address on the profile page otherwise the contact form will not work. If you do not have an email address ask your tutor to help you set one up.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://interneteproot/joebloggs/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/smallistock_000004178977medium.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6\" alt=\"smallistock_000004178977medium\" src=\"http://interneteproot/joebloggs/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/smallistock_000004178977medium-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Learning styles</strong> Description: Information about learning styles and Multiple Intelligence (MI) is helpful for everyone especially for people with learning disabilities and Attention Deficit Disorder. <a title=\"Visit Learning styles\" href=\"http://www.metacafe.com/watch/yt-I39LPOYfE5c/learning_styles\" target=\"_blank\">A short film about learning styles</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>NOTE:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe pages and categories provided are just a starting point. You can develop your own as you go along. Please consult with your tutor before deleting existing categories or pages as some of these may be <em>requirements</em> for the completion of your ePortfolio.\r\n\r\nYou have been provided with many links to useful web pages. You can delete those which are of no use or interest to you. Feel free to create new link categories to organise your own links.\r\n\r\nThere are many useful features in Wordpress to make creating a personalised site easy for you. If you wish to get your own Wordpress hosting account on the Internet, again, consult your tutor.','test post','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-01-14 16:06:12','2014-01-14 16:06:12','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2014-01-14 16:02:58','2014-01-14 16:02:58','<div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Course Details</strong>\r\n\r\nPut the name of the course you are doing and a little information about what happens in each unit in the course.\r\n\r\ne.g.\r\n<strong>NCON Pre-vocational construction</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>D3SJ10</strong> Technical drawing: We learn the basics of creating plans and some maths</li>\r\n	<li><strong>DD2310</strong> Decorative painting: We learn about materials and techniques for decorative painting</li>\r\n	<li>etc….</li>\r\n</ul>\r\ne.g.\r\n<strong>HNC Computing</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>DH2T34</strong> Computer architecture: We do binary arithmetic, logic gates and CPU registers</li>\r\n	<li><strong>DF6035</strong> Internet web development: We do style sheets and learn how to use Dreamweaver</li>\r\n	<li>etc….</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Why am I doing this course?</strong>\r\n\r\nWhat do you hope this course will enable you to do?\r\n\r\n</div>','my course ','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2014-01-14 16:03:57','2014-01-14 16:03:57','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2014-01-14 16:05:51','2014-01-14 16:05:51','','smallistock_000004178977medium','','inherit','open','open','','smallistock_000004178977medium','','','2014-01-14 16:05:51','2014-01-14 16:05:51','',1,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/smallistock_000004178977medium.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(8,1,'2014-01-15 12:56:32','2014-01-15 12:56:32','<div>\r\n\r\nFrom previous experience, here are a few tips for putting together your ePortfolio:\r\n\r\nDon\'t use word-processing software to create your portfolio (Microsoft Word/OpenOffice.org/iWork). There is no need to use anything other than your web browser (Firefox, Internet Explorer, Safari) to make your ePortfolio. There is a facility to paste from word-processor shown as a <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.dgmyspace.dumgal.ac.uk/eportfolios/testportfolio/wp-content/plugins/nds-paste/paste/images/pasteword.gif\" /> when writing a post. If you have some information in a document you wish to transfer into your portfolio but this should be fairly rare.\r\n\r\nDon\'t upload word-processor documents as blog entries. This defeats the purpose of having editing facilities on your portfolio. The search function will not find any text contained in a document either. Also, consider that an employer may not be using the same type of word-processor that you are! Type directly into your web page.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some recommended file types for working on your ePortfolio:\r\n</strong>To show <strong>photos</strong> in your ePortfolio use either <a title=\"jpeg on wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jpeg\">JPEG</a> (typically created by digital cameras) or <a title=\"png files on wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_Network_Graphics\">PNG</a> files (.jpg, .jpeg, .png)\r\n\r\nIf you have photos to put on your ePortfolio (from a digital camera) they need to be resized before use.  If you need to resize your images, try the <a title=\"image resizer\" href=\"http://www.dglearnnet.com/moodle2/apps/imageresizer/imageresizer.php\">automatic ePortfolio image resizer</a> on LearnNet.\r\n\r\nFor <strong>sounds</strong> use <a title=\"mp3 at wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mp3\">mp3</a> files (.mp3).\r\nFor <strong>video</strong> use <strong>mp4</strong> video which is probably already produced by your smartphone or tablet. We have a video converter in College to create flash video from other formats which will also work in your ePortfolio (but may not work for <i>all</i> of your site visitors). Ask your tutor about this if you are having problems with video on your ePortfolio.\r\n\r\n<strong>Never use:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"MS Paint on WikiPedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Paint\">MS Paint</a> (.bmp) - These images are much too large</li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"wav files on wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wav\">WAV Files</a> (.wav) - These sound files are often 10 times larger than mp3 files</li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"avi files on wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AVI\">AVI Files</a> (.avi) - AVI files are too unpredictable to use in your website</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>PS: You can safely delete this post!</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>','dos and donts','','publish','open','open','','dos-and-donts','','','2014-01-23 10:55:09','2014-01-23 10:55:09','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2014-01-15 13:00:22','2014-01-15 13:00:22','<h2>Curriculum Vitae</h2>\r\nPut your personal details on the password protected personal details page, not in this public page.\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Desired employment / Occupational field</strong></td>\r\n<td>(remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Work experience</strong></td>\r\n<td>Add separate entries for each relevant post occupied, starting from the most recent.Dates\r\nOccupation or position held\r\nMain activities and responsibilities\r\nName and address of employer\r\nType of business or sector\r\n\r\n(remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Education and training</strong></td>\r\n<td>Add separate entries for each relevant course you have completed, starting from the most recent.Dates\r\nTitle of qualification awarded\r\nPrincipal subjects/occupational skills covered\r\nName and type of organisation providing education and training\r\nLevel in national or international classification\r\n\r\n(remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Personal skills and competences</strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Social skills and competences</strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Organisational skills and competences</strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Technical skills and competences </strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Computer skills and competences </strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Artistic skills and competences </strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Other skills and competences </strong></td>\r\n<td>Replace this text by a description of these competences and indicate where they were acquired. (Remove if not relevant)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Driving licence </strong></td>\r\n<td>State here whether you hold a driving licence and if so for which categories of vehicle. (Remove if not relevant, see instructions)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Additional information</strong></td>\r\n<td>Include here any other information that may be relevant, for example contact persons, references, etc. (Remove heading if not relevant, see instructions)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nFor examples of completed Europass CVs try <a href=\"http://europass.cedefop.europa.eu/europass/home/hornav/Downloads/EuropassCV/CVExamples.csp\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>\r\n\r\nCV adapted from Europass CV For more information on Europass go to <a href=\"http://europass.cedefop.europa.eu/\" target=\"_blank\">europass.cedefop.europa.eu</a>','my CV','','publish','open','open','','my-cv','','','2014-01-15 13:00:22','2014-01-15 13:00:22','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2014-01-15 13:02:52','2014-01-15 13:02:52','Find out your learning style and write about it here.','my learning style','','publish','open','open','','my-learning-style','','','2014-01-15 13:02:52','2014-01-15 13:02:52','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2014-01-15 13:04:03','2014-01-15 13:04:03','<div>\r\n\r\nThis page is intended to be used to store confidential information. The page is password protected. You are encouraged to change the password once you have updated this page. Referees are included on this page to protect the identity of others online. Remember that your website will be visible on the Internet. You should never put personal details of yourself or others on a web page. The current password is <strong>password</strong>. You can delete this paragraph whenever you like.\r\n\r\n<strong>PERSONAL DETAILS</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Name</strong>\r\nJoe Bloggs\r\n\r\n<strong>Address</strong>\r\n10 Blog Street\r\nBlogtown\r\nBlog Code\r\n\r\n<strong>Date of Birth</strong>\r\n1st January 1900\r\n\r\n<strong>Marital Status </strong>\r\nSingle, Married, Divorced\r\n\r\n<strong>Sex </strong>\r\nMale or Female\r\n\r\n<strong>Telephone Number </strong>\r\n0000 000 0000\r\n\r\n<strong>Email Address</strong>\r\ntestportfolio@dumgal.ac.uk\r\n\r\n<strong>Referees</strong>\r\nPut your references here.\r\n\r\n</div>','Protected: my personal details','','publish','open','open','password','protected-my-personal-details','','','2014-01-15 13:04:03','2014-01-15 13:04:03','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=15',0,'page','',0),(17,1,'2014-01-15 13:05:01','2014-01-15 13:05:01','<strong>Example personal statement - you should replace this with your own</strong>\r\nI have always been interested in the way things work and why they work. I am always determined to succeed and I feel that this course will make the most of my skills. I believe that by the end of this course I will have the skills and knowledge to become a successful …','personal statement','','publish','open','open','','personal-statement','','','2014-01-15 13:05:01','2014-01-15 13:05:01','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=17',0,'page','',0),(19,1,'2014-01-15 13:11:08','2014-01-15 13:11:08','These links may be of use to you creating your ePortfolio:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"BBC - job seeking skills\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/northernireland/schools/11_16/gogetit/index.shtml\">BBC - job seeking skills</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"David Tennant ePortfolio\" href=\"http://www.dgmyspace.dumgal.ac.uk/eportfolios/DavidTennant\">David Tennant ePortfolio</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Honey &amp; Mumford\'s Learning Styles\" href=\"http://www.brainboxx.co.uk/A2_LEARNSTYLES/pages/learningstyles.htm\">Honey &amp; Mumford\'s Learning Styles</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"My World of Work\" href=\"http://www.myworldofwork.co.uk/\">My World of Work</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Study Skills 16+\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/schools/websites/16/site/study_skills.shtml\">Study Skills 16+</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Time Management\" href=\"http://www.mdx.ac.uk/www/study/Timetips.htm\">Time Management</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"What Am I Like?\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/science/humanbody/mind/surveys/whatamilike/\">What Am I Like?</a></li>\r\n</ul>','useful links','','publish','open','open','','useful-links','','','2014-01-15 13:11:08','2014-01-15 13:11:08','',0,'http://interneteproot/joebloggs/?page_id=19',0,'page','',0);
